    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "3 Mar 50",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Reference our TX AJACI-1-2, 2nd Mar supplementar",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "report follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "1. (A) At 2130 hours on 2nd Mar radar station",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "picked up 2 objects 310 degrees, altitude 80000 feet, ap-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "proximately 18 miles from Knoxville in general direction of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Oak Ridge, moving in circular motion but in opposite direc-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "tions.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "(B) At 2230 hours 2nd Mar and again at 0030 hours",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "3rd Mar station picked up object, moving same direction,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "locality and altitude.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "(C) Density of object similar to DC-3 airplane,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "speed not established but report as \"terrific\".",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "2. CIA Radar Technician reportedly arrived Knoxville",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "today to check radar set and operation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "3. Arrangement reportedly made by FBI with Naval",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "and Marine Reserve Unit Knoxville to set up radar equipment",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "to verify reception of VROL radar station.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "4. All information on this subject this headquarters",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "has been turned over to A-2 Fourteenth Air Force.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
